Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從第一眼看到妳之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.53,0:00:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡妳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.56,0:00:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.76,0:00:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.43,0:00:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎…?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.31,0:01:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是認真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身上並沒有具體的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.75,0:01:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有“這個”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.16,0:01:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有“這個”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加速吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加速吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.51,0:01:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超越音速
